Sales Register =========== Ctrl + B = Barcode Cursor
F6 = Increase Item Qty (+) F7 = Decrease item Qty (-) F4 = Selected Item Delete
Shift + C = Cash sale Ctrl + S = Sale Save only Ctrl + Enter = Complete Sale and print Shift + Delete = Clear items from cart
Menu ===================== Alt + S = Open Sales Register Ctrl + Q = Quick Sale window Ctrl + A = Add new item Ctrl + I = Stock item list Ctrl + D = Due List Ctrl + K = Kitchen Display Ctrl + E = Employee Ctrl + R = Report
F1 = Help F2 = About us
